'''Nicandra Plaza''' was an area of the [[Senate District/Legends|Senate District]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It bordered [[Hospital Plaza]] and contained the [[Nicandra Counterrevolutionary Signalmen's Memorial Building/Legends|Nicandra Counterrevolutionary Signalmen's Memorial Building]].

